SELECT
  a/data[at0001]/events[at0002]/data[at0003]/items[at0004]/value as T0_body_segment_name,
  a/data[at0001]/events[at0002]/data[at0003]/items[at0005]/value as T0_laterality,
  a/data[at0001]/events[at0002]/data[at0003]/items[at0008]/value as T0_circumference
FROM
  EHR e CONTAINS COMPOSITION c CONTAINS (
    OBSERVATION a[openEHR-EHR-OBSERVATION.body_segment_circumference.v1]
  )
WHERE
  a/data[at0001]/events[at0002]/data[at0003]/items[at0004]/value/defining_code/code_string = 'at0019'
ORDER BY
  c/context/start_time/value DESC LIMIT 1
